## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="767c0-102">的输入模式 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> 由其 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Mode%2A> 属性确定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="767c0-102">The input mode for an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> is determined by its <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Mode%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="767c0-103">默认输入模式为 Voice，这表示由定义的语法 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> 将匹配语音输入。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="767c0-103">The default input mode is Voice, which indicates that the grammar defined by the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> will match speech input.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="767c0-104">Dtmf 模式指示语法将匹配双色调多频率 (DTMF) 音而不是语音。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="767c0-104">The Dtmf mode indicates that a grammar will match Dual-Tone Multi-Frequency (DTMF) tones instead of speech.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="767c0-105">有16个 DTMF 音，其中有12个，通常在大多数电话上都找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="767c0-105">There are 16 DTMF tones, 12 of which are commonly found on most telephones.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="767c0-106">当你从创建 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> 对象时 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> ， <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> 对象将与属性指定的输入类型匹配 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Mode%2A> ，后者将获取的实例 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsGrammarMode> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="767c0-106">When you create a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> object from an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>, the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> object will match the type of input specified by the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Mode%2A> property, which gets an instance of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsGrammarMode>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```csharp  
string srgsDocumentFile = Path.Combine(Path.GetTempPath(), "srgsDocumentFile.xml");  
SrgsDocument document = null;  
GrammarBuilder builder = null;  
Grammar grammar = null;  
  
Choices firstThree = new Choices(new string[] {"1", "2", "3"});  
Choices nextThree = new Choices(new string[] {"4", "5", "6"});  
Choices lastThree = new Choices(new string[] {"7", "8", "9"});  
  
Choices keyPadChoices = new Choices(new GrammarBuilder[] {firstThree, nextThree, lastThree, new Choices("0")});  
  
builder = new GrammarBuilder(keyPadChoices);  
document = new SrgsDocument(builder);  
  
document.Mode = SrgsGrammarMode.Dtmf;  
grammar = new Grammar(document);   
```
